title: Garmin MapSource Ukraine: Dnepr and Dunaj (Danube) v2.00uL
description:
Garmin MapSource Ukraine: Dnepr & Danube river v.2.00uL

New map of the pond of the Dnepr and of the Danube river.
Detailed map of entire river the Dnepr and part of Danube where it passes through Ukrainen territory.
They are added on the map:
- basic ship motion
- additional ship motion
- buoys of the ship motion
- buoys of the separation of the ship motion
- mark of the depth
- isobath
- island, piers
- places dangerous for the floating (banks, stones, the flooded cuttings down) 

Maps include detailed information about the coastline, the islands, the depths (point marks and the contour line of depth), the heights (point marks and the contour line of heights on dry land), the vegetation (including the form of vegetation), POIs, bases of leisure, forestry and so forth, coastal road net and much other.
